Galaxy Gold's Founder, CEO Peter Skeat Steps Down, Becomes a Non-Executive

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-02-28T12:33:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-28/galaxy-gold-s-founder-ceo-peter-skeat-steps-down-becomes-a-non-executive.html
Galaxy Gold Mining Ltd. said founder
and Chief Executive Officer Peter Skeat has stepped down and
will become a non-executive director.  Non-executive Chairman Ian Watson has been appointed
executive chairman with immediate effect and “assumes day-to-
day responsibility for the affairs of the company,” the gold
miner said in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  